title: TradingView Chart Integration
tags: [[GettingStarted]] [[AI Supply Chain]]
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

The AI supply-chain node tiddlers include embedded TradingView charts for every ticker that can be mapped to a TradingView symbol.

Implementation notes:

* Uses TradingView iframe widgets, not external scripts, because TiddlyWiki blocks `script` tags as unsafe.
* Each node keeps its illustrative ticker list in the `tickers` field.
* Nodes with recognized tickers also get a `tradingview-symbols` field.
* Charts are live/delayed from TradingView when the tiddler is opened; data is not stored in the wiki.
* Some private, non-US, or ambiguous company names are left as text only until mapped manually.

Examples:

* [[AI Supply Chain: AI Accelerators]]
* [[AI Supply Chain: Hyperscalers / Cloud Providers]]
* [[AI Supply Chain: Lithography Tools]]
* [[AI Supply Chain: Electric Grid]]

Ticker/company lists are examples only, not investment advice.
